column5: I haven't caught any whities or lakers this year as I have only been out a couple of times.  I have caught many perch but tomorrow I got the go ahead from the boss at home to go for some trout one last time.  I will be out from 7:33 until 11:46 am.  I hope to get this trout skunk off my back.
Best of luck.  I've been up there 4 times for whities, and only have two myself.
Good luck tomorrow Cudz , but be careful out on the ice!!

Sounds like my record Cudz!!  Been out on Nipissing...2 full days of ice fishing and nothing.  Last weekend I had 3 on at Simcoe, iced none.  I'm heading out tomorrow as well, hoping to finally get a whitie!!!  Good luck!  733 til 1146?  Well, that's the problem, they start biting at 1150.
